Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- A heat source?\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sovereign Degwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can achieve peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sovereign Degwin!\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the Revil Fleet's\Nmain forces are located!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not all of them are gone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all of them are gone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Space Fortress: A Baoa Qu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Solar Ray has been fired at Gel Dorva!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, you heard that, right?\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you check the laser sensors?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard, all right.\NDid you hear at your station, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at level two battle stations.\NIdle chatter is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Degwin's identification signal\Nwas detected at the Gel Dorva line...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Degwin...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And it was at the exact same point\Nthat the enemy fleet was situated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we notified about the Great Degwin\Nheading into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain surveillance\Non the enemy's remaining forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we wiped out even half of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Degwin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the Saffron is left\Nfrom the 12th Division!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Cisco's damaged too!\N- We have only 8 ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are damaged quite badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fraw Bow!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Any word from the Luzal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The main fleet has been ordered\Nto gather around the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Have you heard anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! They seem to be\Nin a state of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention White Base crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone stand by at level 2 battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you figure anything out?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They used something like the Solar System.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Solar System?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation used it at Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this one's much more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}White Base! Security code Beta Trois!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brave and loyal Zeon soldiers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Half of the Federation fleet has been\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This brilliant light is proofi\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the massive damage thatstained...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...no matter how much fighting strength{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...It Is of little consequence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dare I say it. debris!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I declare it impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...for this weak host of enemies\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the control of we, the chosen\Nsuperior race of Zeon, humanity can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...at last ensure its eternal survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If this war drags on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...it will pose a threat to humanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We must teach the incompetents\Nof the Earth Federation a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time for humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...to stand and face\Nthe future that awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Second and third battalions\Nwill advance from N Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We will gather all remaining ships,\Nwith the Luzal as our flagship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...and proceed from S Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We obviously lack fighting strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could use our Solar System too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that A Baoa Qu's firepower\Nis greatest where we want to attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's also their weakest point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that Newtype intuition?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to synchronize timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1... 0! Operation starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands go to level 1 battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll break through the F-line in 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't waste our lives over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Fraw Bow I know.\NWell, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro, don't do anything crazy.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be right there!\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're heading back to E-Block!\N- Good luck, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's Hayato?\N- He's stuck on Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creepy laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not hurting anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good luck!\N- We believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said back there... Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If Newtypes could predict the future,\Nthen we all wouldn't have to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If Amuro hadn't said what he did,\Nthe crew would've abandoned ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,From fear, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't become gods\Neven if they try with all their might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy's creating a\Nbeam interference field...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond with missiles.\NDon't move our mobile suits yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The carrier Dolos is on schedule.\NHold off for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Reroute half the vessels in S Field\Nover to N Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad for having lost their main forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gwazine entering E Field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's likely Rear Admiral Kycilia's vessel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Reroute it now to N Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The doesn't match the number of ships\Nthat Kycilia set out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of the new Gelgoog types\Nhas been dispatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left for me to pilot, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to try out the Zeong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it's only\N80 percent complete, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit that partially...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...incorporates the psycommu system\Ndeveloped for the Elmeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it has the Braw Bro's characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone has launched in the Zeong.\NGive it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, I'll go see Gihren.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,80 percent, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magellan-class destroyed, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy mobile suit forces have launched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Dolos. Don't fail me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kycilia has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize profusely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Elmeth was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it couldn't even handle a single Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use the Zeong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That incomplete model?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't defeat the Gundam unless\Nwe use somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...who might be a Newtype.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Char... once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolos is advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Degwin. Where is it deployed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it at Z um City?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was destroyed.\NIt moved out too far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Did Sovereign Degwin\Nlend you his ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kycilia. Do you think our father\Nwould hand over the Great Degwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our forces are simply overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,80 percent complete?\NYou've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In its current state,\Nthe Zeong can fight at 100 percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has no legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Legs are just for show!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The brass doesn't understand things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You explained how to operate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But the psycommu...\NDo you think I can handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Newtype abilities\Nare unknown, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't guarantee anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're very frank. I don't appreciate it.\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If it makes you feel any better, Captain,\NI'm sure you'll do well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your numbers are\Ntoo small to attack us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dolos is holding its ground quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Send all N Field fleets forward and...\N- A new fleet? A Federation Forces one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the N Field line.\NWe're gathering data now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation's fighting well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's merely the last futile effort of\Ntheir surviving forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status of Captain Char's Zeong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Yes? the Zeong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's good to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... A new enemy fleet\Nwas discovered in S Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after them with\Nthe 34th Mobile Suit Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Ma'am! We'll take outeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation won't have\Nany more forces in reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to defend S Field\Nwith our current strength, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who killed his own father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now. The question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...whether or not I actually have\Ndefinite Newtype potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Elevate 2 degrees! Retreat!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! A mobile suit team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's strong! Is it Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's behind me?! What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A Newtype who's stronger than Char! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But landing on A Baoa Qu\Nis more important now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My true enemy is within there.\NAnd it's not Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the Dolos forces\Nwill take care of N Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Father was aboard the Great Degwin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you destroyed it along\Nwith the Federation Forces. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing would have resulted from\Nan ill-timed peace initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no need to let him die...\N"Supreme Commander".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of the jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How surprisingly naive, my dear brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Supreme Commander Gihren?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of the body now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a supreme commander\Ncan't get away with patricide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of you disagree, you can\Nfile charges after the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander Gihren\Ndied honorably in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dolos fleet has been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kycilia, your orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twanning. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take over command of A Baoa Qu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch mobile suit forces to N Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status of S Field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've eliminated\N10 of the enemy's 25 vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other vessels are\Nhanging on in S Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Send Char's Zeong to the front line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate mobile suit forces in S Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those new models are quite something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Sayla to keep her G-Fighter\Nnear the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! The enemy's defense seemed\Nto weaken momentarily just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That was rather strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be struggling,\Nbut from the looks of it, so are they.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pathetic. I've lost sight of the Gundam.\NWhere is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy mobile suits\Nhave landed in N Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. That's a concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How's S Field holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the Gundam\Nhas broken through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And Char's Zeong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Obstructed by the enemy,\Nand can't get close to the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his first time in the Zeong, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char! I think he found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see him! I can see my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Gelgoogs and Doms aren't\Ndoing well. Why is that, Twanning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am! It appears that many\Nof the pilots are student recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Students?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I assure you,\Nthey've been fully trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the outcome I'm concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they're just too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But their patriotic spirit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the Supreme Commander had\Ntaken notice of Newtypes earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw the enemy into A Baoa Qu\Nso we can pick them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't too many of the enemy left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to show up here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,From the other direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He dodged me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Char was beginning to feel intense alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeong had been\Ndeveloped for Newtypes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he was frustrated by his inability\Nto draw out its full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam pilot was unquestionably\Ndriving him into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely I must be a Newtype too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The finale is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro and Char duel without mobile suits.\NThis is no longer a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the fate imposed on Newtypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the red flames of A Baoa Qu\Nengulf the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NEscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:54.99,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:59.99,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:10.21,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:15.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:19.76,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:25.15,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:29.73,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:40.04,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:54.99,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:59.99,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:10.21,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:15.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:19.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:25.15,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:29.73,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:40.04,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
